      "content": "so you're saying focus on the people first. but doesn't that just push off the inevitable fiscal collapse? isn't it kind of irresponsible to keep borrowing more just to fund welfare when the debt scales up, potentially bankrupting future generations? wouldn't that actually be more \"harmful\" in the long run than the short-term suffering you mentioned?",
